{"id": 435, "genre": 1001, "title": "父母给你介绍的相亲对象大概都是啥样的?", "description": "听起来永远优秀到开挂，吓得我一个都没敢见。", "record_count": 1892, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606161854rFWGg9bwXS3K1nUz.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-07-20T15:51:20Z", "options": [{"id": 4334, "content": "人好 漂亮 职业好 家境好", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145902}, {"id": 4336, "content": "见了面才知道自己在介绍人眼里是什么货色了…", "image": "img/option/option/20160606144915qj76TxaFBRAu91sD.jpg", "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145901}, {"id": 4006, "content": "可能是个没跟父母摊牌的Gay", "image": null, "praise_count": 188, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4007, "content": "“家里（重音）很有钱”", "image": null, "praise_count": 73, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4009, "content": "“年轻有为”，一个借家里钱正要改变世界的创业者", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4124, "content": "“人很好，特别老实，念书的时候成绩很好，内向没谈过恋爱”……丑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 382, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118131}, {"id": 4125, "content": "人老实钱多家境好", "image": null, "praise_count": 168, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4126, "content": "性格古怪，不会聊天，一副“整个世界和我无关”的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 3660}, {"id": 4160, "content": "打字员，20元2千字,4000字=40元，以此类推，上不封顶，手 机电 脑均可。在家 即可，3500保 底，QQ：876988151 此处不回", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145247}, {"id": 4161, "content": "和爸爸妈妈是世交", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126177}, {"id": 4189, "content": "不知道是和家人沟通太少，还是他们想要把我嫁掉的心非常急切，相亲的对象，完全看不上眼！完全！", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145248}, {"id": 4269, "content": "会做生意", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138168}, {"id": 4243, "content": "国企待遇好—过年发年货多两箱猪蹄儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145609}, {"id": 4206, "content": "这年头，好男孩早就被抢光了，只剩这个", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142413}, {"id": 4210, "content": "查他怕特他怕她说怕他怕啊怕怕他怕他他他他他特他怕踏踏特他怕踏踏补补啊怕他怕他怕啊他怕特她惹她怕他怕怕他怕特怕怕他怕阿萨踏踏啪啪啪啪啪啪啪特特她怕他啪啪啪啪啪啪他怕他怕他怕怕怕怕怕踏踏塞车排插怕热任姐深蓝色怕圈圈热死了惹她go代表", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144866}, {"id": 4215, "content": "正式工", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145578}, {"id": 4216, "content": "你不喜欢的样", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 3797}, {"id": 4382, "content": "反正。。。比我好就对了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146144}, {"id": 4387, "content": "奥迪女！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 6042, "content": "没房子？租一个；工资不高？工作稳定就行；离过婚？没孩子就行。我忍不住问我妈，我是你亲生的么？我，只是不想将就，就为了找到对的那个。", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234845RjlboONE7LY830Js.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137688}, {"id": 8203, "content": "爸妈选完再到你选", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161347}, {"id": 4368, "content": "漂亮，心地善良，性格开朗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146092}, {"id": 7702, "content": "七大姑八大姨朋友家孩子，没结过婚，有个好工作，你俩正好一对。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158342}, {"id": 4127, "content": "活在自己世界里的正常人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 86709}, {"id": 4128, "content": "先聊聊，没准有感觉呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 121, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4129, "content": "一个省的，近！", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1065}, {"id": 4130, "content": "有钱又帅还顾家，男人三十没结婚，不是基佬还是什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 117, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4131, "content": "我是全世界最好的男纸，单身原因是没有人能配得上我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 106877}, {"id": 4132, "content": "遇到新东方厨师就嫁了吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138553}, {"id": 4134, "content": "庄户地的就行。咱要求不高", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 128838}, {"id": 4135, "content": "老实，有房，大公司，以前学习成绩蛮好的，跟他爸妈知根知底（还能更无聊吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 89, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 4136, "content": "钻石王老五呗", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135699}, {"id": 4138, "content": "@mg 最有权力回答这个问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1}, {"id": 4139, "content": "“银行里做的哦很好的哦。”“？？...我看上去像是会喜欢...？？”“嘁。至少人家工资比你多吧。”“......”（非爸妈）", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 26306}, {"id": 4141, "content": "      就是胖点，，，人也不丑，。???。", "image": "img/option/option/20160606144915Ud82goVTabz5DjeF.jpg", "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 50612}, {"id": 4146, "content": "没给介绍", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 99741}, {"id": 4158, "content": "一直以为 自己只会喜欢女人 原来也喜欢男人 双性恋", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 98878}, {"id": 4159, "content": "工作好-银行的，要求高-至今没嫁，人老实-其实贵圈很乱！", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145305}, {"id": 19776, "content": "她对我说：你算什么东西？看都没看过就说不见。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259101}, {"id": 7233, "content": "年轻多金 早早秃顶", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155057}, {"id": 11087, "content": "不是那个嫌我丑、就是这个我嫌丑，分分合合、互做备胎 …", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 150923}, {"id": 6751, "content": "介绍人不靠谱，对方情况怎么样他们自己都不清楚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152398}, {"id": 15203, "content": "有份稳定的工作，父母讲道理", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149312}, {"id": 4218, "content": "和那个谁（我前任）长的像?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 59053}, {"id": 16783, "content": "从没有过！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 242160}, {"id": 4004, "content": "公务员，公务员，公务员", "image": null, "praise_count": 148, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 6820, "content": "我未成年", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137632}, {"id": 4008, "content": "“在北京/上海有房”", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 8373, "content": "聊过印象不错，但没有再联系！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162958}, {"id": 4287, "content": "都看脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117090}]}